.ie n .IP "$TMPDIR" 9
.el .IP "\f(CW$TMPDIR\fR" 9
.IX Item "$TMPDIR"
Directory for temporary files used for time synchronization.
.SH "CONFIG FILE"
.IX Header "CONFIG FILE"
The file ~/.ftpsync/config
